abstract.text: Representation of mDL document
The city where the mDL holder lives.
Country subdivision code of the jurisdiction that issued the mDL. The first part of the code shall be the same as the value for issuing country.
Date of expiry of eDL (physical document) issued to mDL holder
Driver’s restrictions
A reproduction of the mDL holder’s portrait.
The year when the mDL holder was born.  Age attestation: In what year where you born?
Alpha-2 country code of the issuing authority’s country or territory.
The framework for acting as a Mobile Driving Licence (mDL) Reader compliant with ISO/IEC 18013-5.
Day, month and year on which the mDL holder was born. If unknown, approximate date of birth.
The age of the mDL holder.  Age attestation: How old are you (in years)?
mDL holder’s eye colour. The value shall be one of the following: “black”, “blue”, “brown”, “dichromatic”, “grey”, “green”, “hazel”, “maroon”, “pink”, “unknown”.
Image of the signature or usual mark of the mDL holder.
Age attestation: Nearest “true” attestation above request.
The postal code of the mDL holder.
The state/province/district where the mDL holder lives.
Permanent place of residence. The place where the mDL holder resides and/or may be contacted (street/house number, municipality etc.).
The country where the mDL holder lives as the two letter country code.
mDL holder’s national ID or alien ID, or diplomatic ID
mDL holder’s height in centimeters.
First name(s), other name(s), or secondary identifier, of the mDL holder.
mDL holder’s sex.
mDL holder’s blood group
Date when mDL expires.
An audit control number assignet by the issuing authority.
Nationality of the mDL holder as two letter country code.
The family name of the mDL holder using full UTF-8 character set.
The given name of the mDL holder using full UTF-8 character set.
Representation of mDL document
mDL holder’s hair colour. One of these values: “bald”, “black”, “blond”, “brown”, “grey”, “red”, “auburn”, “sandy”, “white”, “unknown”.
mDL holder’s weigth in kilograms.
The number assigned or calculated by the issuing authority.
Date when portrait was taken.
Issuing authority name.
Country and municipality or state/province where the mDL holder was born.
Date of issue of eDL (physical document) issued to mDL holder
Driving privileges of the mDL holder. Categories of vehicles/restrictions/conditions. (zero or more)
UN Distinguishing sign.
Date when mDL was issued.
Last name, surname or primary identifier, of the mDL holder.
